ZH: 我需要报销这次差旅费。
EN: I need to reimburse this business trip expense.

ZH: 请将火车票的发票拿给财务部门报销。
EN: Please submit the train ticket receipt to the finance department for reimbursement.

ZH: 我的手机话费可以报销吗？
EN: Can I be reimbursed for my cellphone bill?

ZH: 请填写完整的报销申请表格。
EN: Please fill out the reimbursement application form completely.

ZH: 我会及时审批你的报销申请。
EN: I will approve your reimbursement request promptly.

ZH: 报销金额将会在下个工作日转到你的银行账户。
EN: The reimbursement amount will be transferred to your bank account by the next business day.

ZH: 请务必保存好原始的费用收据以备报销。
EN: Please make sure to keep the original expense receipts for reimbursement.

ZH: 你可以通过电子邮件提交报销资料。
EN: You can submit the reimbursement documents via email.

ZH: 报销政策会在公司内网上找到。
EN: The reimbursement policy can be found on the company intranet.

ZH: 请确保报销资料的准确性和合法性。
EN: Please ensure the accuracy and legality of the reimbursement documents.

ZH: 我需要你在三天内完成报销流程。
EN: I need you to complete the reimbursement process within three days.

ZH: 每月底前必须提交报销报表。
EN: The reimbursement report must be submitted by the end of each month.

ZH: 他向公司报销了加班的车费。
EN: He reimbursed the company for the overtime taxi fare.

ZH: 请跟踪你的报销进度并及时提供必要的文件。
EN: Please track your reimbursement progress and provide the necessary documents in a timely manner.

ZH: 报销申请需要主管审批后才能生效。
EN: The reimbursement request needs to be approved by the supervisor before it takes effect.

ZH: 我们的报销流程需要优化。
EN: Our reimbursement process needs to be optimized.

ZH: 报销款项将在下个月的工资单中反映。
EN: The reimbursement amount will be reflected in next month's paycheck.

ZH: 希望公司能加大报销额度。
EN: I hope the company can increase the reimbursement limit.

ZH: 他忘记报销邮寄资料的成本。
EN: He forgot to reimburse the cost of mailing the documents.

ZH: 我们的报销政策已经更新。
EN: Our reimbursement policy has been updated.
